{"tid":163042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Google搜尋超神！ 美國母子失散19年終於重逢","createTime":"2017-03-19T16:41:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-20T02:03:55.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8184125954483dca204795f4149a2ff52a8a1627","tid":163042,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T16:41:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpoqbqmn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpoqbqmn.jpg&h=50065d98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">哈迪（左3）意外與母親（左4）重逢。（圖擷自每日郵報）</span><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕果然是Google大神！美國北卡羅萊納州一名媽媽與兒子失散19年，日前她突發奇想用谷歌（Google）搜尋自己兒子的名字，沒想到最後真的意外找到對方，兩人相隔19年再度重逢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/2017/new/mar/19/images/bigPic/400_400/phpz7conA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2F2017%2Fnew%2Fmar%2F19%2Fimages%2FbigPic%2F400_400%2Fphpz7conA.jpg&h=7c6a91ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">哈迪與家人打成一片。（圖擷自每日郵報）</span><br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，北卡一名媽媽柏蘭（Amanda Borland）17歲時產下兒子哈迪（Jibril Hardy），但因為無法扶養只好將他送到德州的收養家庭，隨後雙方因故失去連繫長達19年。<br />\n柏蘭始終沒有忘記親生兒子，去年開始尋找哈迪的下落，她花了整整一年時間，在一次用Google搜尋時，刻意改變「德州」的拼寫方式，沒想到真的找到親生兒子。她表示，第一眼看到哈迪時就直接飆淚，並說自己很驚訝。哈迪則說，自己的養父母很高興，他能夠找到親生家庭。<br />\n隨後哈迪也前往北卡拜訪親生母親，他表示自己在17歲才知道被收養，唯一知道親生父母的是他們的名字，但姓氏和其他訊息都不知道。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2009760\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2009760&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6o9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=964fd265\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2009760&h=8d53b2aa\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2009760</a>"},{"pid":"c74678be20f41c886e370a18a5efe6bd66eef219","tid":163042,"uid":31752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T16:56:17.000Z","msg":"串錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd586d0013e6f3e2fc86bf9880838ba9d937d4ed","tid":163042,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T19:09:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ba67ef73fc32fe70a53328e837f5f5500d1d16f","tid":163042,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T19:16:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"081953e7433c24461a56efdd62ca32edc2a011ea","tid":163042,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T01:45:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3fc4f7edb85f6e8dbc9b9c6a9dc5c678f053a97","tid":163042,"uid":46328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T02:03:55.000Z","msg":"假新聞"}]}